last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 10
last_episode_to_air.overview: Dong-ha returns home to find the police digging around.  Kwang-chul sends the head cartel a bloody message.  Joo-hyun takes matters into her own hands.

name: A Model Family
overview: After unwittingly stealing money from a cartel, a cash-strapped professor finds the only way to save his broken family is by working as a drug courier.
tagline: Dare Not Desire The Money Of The Dead

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: After losing hope of gaining tenure, a desperate Park Dong-ha acts quickly when he comes across a van containing two dead bodies and a bag of cash.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Ma Kwang-chul moves into the neighborhood, with Kwang Joo-hyun soon following suit.  Dong-ha searches online for tips on how to launder money.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Kwang-chul uncovers useful information on what went down with the money launderer.  Dong-ha calls the police with an anonymous tip about his neighbor.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Dong-ha sets out for Busan to make his first delivery.  Kang Eun-ju searches the streets for her daughter, who refuses to come home.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Park Yeon-woo stirs up trouble for herself and her father after he discovers the hidden bag and takes off with a chunk of the loot.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Eun-ju trails after Dong-ha as he heads to a spa.  Striking out on his own, Kwang-chul fights for a chance to work for the head cartel.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Kwang-chul drops by to give Tonh-soo a promised heads-up.  Park Deuk-soo makes himself at home while stealthily looking for clues.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Dong-ha and a partner are tasked with transporting the cash.  Choi-Kang-jun offers to free Dong-ha from the money and Kwang-chul in one fell swoop.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Fearing for his life, Yong-soo goes into hiding.  Joo-hyn makes Kang-jun an offer in exchange for the identity of the mole.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Dong-ha returns home to find the police digging around.  Kwang-chul sends the head cartel a bloody message.  Joo-hyun takes matters into her own hands.
